title: Previewing 'The Challenge: Double Agents' With Bill Simmons and David Jacoby
description:
Bill Simmons and David Jacoby preview the new season of 'The Challenge: Double Agent' by going over the most important contestants on the season.

You can find Bill Simmons and David Jacoby breaking down 'The Challenge' on Wednesdays at 6:30 p.m. PT on the 'Ringer Dish' feed.
